        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "What does a barber shop do?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "Australian barber shops range from traditional old-school shops with hot towel shaves to modern style bars offering fades, designs, and grooming services. Whether you want a classic short back and sides or a contemporary skin fade, there's a barber for you."
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "What should I look for in a barber shop?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "Walk-in vs booking \u2014 some barbers are walk-in only, while others take appointments Ask about their specialties \u2014 fades, razor work, and beard grooming are all distinct skills Check if they offer hot towel shaves (not all barbers do anymore) Look at recent reviews mentioning the specific barber you'd see"
          }
        },
